<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="nb">sudo </span>apt <span class="nb">install </span>tor torsocks</code></pre></figure>

<p>you will need to configure torify check https://www.linux.com/blog/beginners-guide-tor-ubuntu</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">torify whois 25.166.194.172</code></pre></figure>

